body:
When you use the `protobuf` version 3.7 compiled proto file contains the following content:

```
#ifndef PROTOBUF_INCLUDED_PulsarApi_2eproto
#define PROTOBUF_INCLUDED_PulsarApi_2eproto

#include <limits>
#include <string>

#include <google/protobuf/port_def.inc> // key point
#if PROTOBUF_VERSION < 3007000
```

 this is not recognized in `protoc 2.6.1`
